<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Mission & Vision — STP</title>

<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #0e1217;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        background: #161b22;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(40,199,111,0.2);
        animation: fade 1s ease;
    }

    h1, h2 {
        color: #28c76f;
    }

    @keyframes fade {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>Mission & Vision — Save The Planet</h1>

<h2>Mission</h2>
<p>To unite people and technologies worldwide to heal our planet through a blockchain-powered eco-economy.</p>

<h2>Vision</h2>
<p>A global ecosystem where humanity restores the environment and is rewarded for real positive actions.</p>

<h2>Core Goals</h2>
<ul>
<li>Reduce global pollution</li>
<li>Create transparent eco-financing</li>
<li>Support eco-startups</li>
<li>Build a sustainable green economy</li>
</ul>

</div>
</body>
</html>
